    "description": "&quot;The Spell Brigade&quot;是一款适合 1-4 名玩家的在线合作 survivors-like 游戏。与你的巫师朋友组队，杀死成群的黑暗生物。完成以团队为基础的目标，解锁新的升级，创造超强的法术协同效果。在这个友谊之火的子弹地狱中，朋友和敌人都是安全的！<br><br><strong>合作友情炮火地狱</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002370/extras/d217584728a7a153759669aba3ff30c5.poster.avif?t=1726642953\" width=598 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002370/extras/d217584728a7a153759669aba3ff30c5.webm?t=1726642953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002370/extras/d217584728a7a153759669aba3ff30c5.mp4?t=1726642953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>法术军团》将您喜爱的幸存者类游戏与疯狂的多人游戏完美结合。一起对抗成千上万的怪兽。一起完成任务和升级法术。共同生存！<br><br><strong>有了这些朋友...</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002370/extras/d0c7692dadacaa285d888f85ac47cbd4.poster.avif?t=1726642953\" width=598 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002370/extras/d0c7692dadacaa285d888f85ac47cbd4.webm?t=1726642953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002370/extras/d0c7692dadacaa285d888f85ac47cbd4.mp4?t=1726642953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>与整支军队作战是一件很冒险的事情。组建你的旅团，一起踏上这条神秘的征途。团队作战有很多好处，但你们难免会踩到对方的脚趾。但不用担心！即使是最不幸、最可怕的死亡，也能通过巫术和友谊的力量得到补救！<br><br><strong>法术队</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002370/extras/ba41231aeac02c00d25de8a84710e592.poster.avif?t=1726642953\" width=598 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002370/extras/ba41231aeac02c00d25de8a84710e592.webm?t=1726642953\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3002370/extras/ba41231aeac02c00d25de8a84710e592.mp4?t=1726642953\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>。<br>寻找、升级并将您的法术与强大的元素相结合。一切都会相互配合，确保没有两个构建是相同的。将这一点与你队伍中的魔法师数量相乘，纯粹、疯狂混乱的潜力将无穷无尽！<br><br><strong> 我们正在努力将我们的游戏发布到 Early Access 中。本演示包含以下内容：</strong>[列表]<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 个可玩的魔法师<br></li><li>1个世界和任务<br></li><li>5种敌人类型<br></li><li>6种元素中的6种法术[/list］</li></ul>",
